{"id": "1506644244713050192", "channel_id": "1506644244713050192", "type": 0, "author_id": "1356970554027933877", "author_name": "calmdreab", "author_bot": false, "content": "⚠️戈利亚×凯刻斯CP向⚠️\nCan you walk on the water if I, you and I\n你能与我在水上行走吗 你和我一起\nBecause your blood's running cold outside the familiar true to life\n因为你流淌的冰冷血液诉说了生命通晓的真理\nCan you walk on the water if I, you and I\n你能与我在水上行走吗 你和我一起\nOr keep your eyes on the road and live the familiar without you and I\n还是让你的双眼保持在路上 住在那没有我们的熟悉地方\n——Agnes Obel《Familiär》\n私人约稿禁一切\nuid100010333", "timestamp": "2026-05-20T13:06:20.036000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "1nekodrool", "emoji_id": "1206774407562006600", "count": 2}, {"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [{"id": "1506644245069562017", "filename": "Image_1779248249907.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 894536, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1506644244713050192/1506644245069562017/Image_1779248249907.png?ex=6a0f034c&is=6a0db1cc&hm=7523034c0e12d92a17c9b9123ed2636a6a6260bf4dd165c212df0c603db70a26&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1506644244713050192", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "【2026戈利亚生贺17h/21:00】Familiär", "forum_channel_id": "1174185304027045969", "thread_tags": ["1441261039227240468"], "is_thread_starter": true}
{"id": "1506628024030986361", "channel_id": "1506628024030986361", "type": 0, "author_id": "1356970554027933877", "author_name": "calmdreab", "author_bot": false, "content": "⚠️戈利亚×凯刻斯CP向⚠️\nI want to be free\n我想要自由\nI want to to be free without my pain\n想要自由而不再痛苦\nI want to see dreams\n我想看到梦想成真\nSea of dreams\n在梦想之海遨游\nPlease stand by me\n请支持我\n——Rauf&Faik《ДОМ》\n私人约稿禁一切\nuid100010333", "timestamp": "2026-05-20T12:01:52.724000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}, {"emoji": "1nekodrool", "emoji_id": "1206774407562006600", "count": 1}], "attachments": [{"id": "1506628024739565670", "filename": "Image_1779248243024.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 1571383, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1506628024030986361/1506628024739565670/Image_1779248243024.png?ex=6a0ef430&is=6a0da2b0&hm=6b218920396b9691e153cb8312545aeed0b7913140978ca5cb909b1c00aba093&"}, {"id": "1506628025515774095", "filename": "Image_1779248243703.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 1672401, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1506628024030986361/1506628025515774095/Image_1779248243703.png?ex=6a0ef431&is=6a0da2b1&hm=a4b15ff373f831ff63403bc3e40778a3f438827f4036500ea8ecaf48f1813dbc&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1506628024030986361", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "【戈利亚生贺17h/20:00】ДОМ", "forum_channel_id": "1174185304027045969", "thread_tags": ["1441261039227240468"], "is_thread_starter": true}
{"id": "1506619485262708889", "channel_id": "1506619485262708889", "type": 0, "author_id": "1356970554027933877", "author_name": "calmdreab", "author_bot": false, "content": "⚠️戈利亚×凯刻斯CP向⚠️\nLady, running down to the riptide\n女孩，奔向潮流所向的地方\nTaken away to the dark side\n被裹挟至黑暗的那一面\nI wanna be your left hand man\n我想要成为牵着你左手的男人\nI love you when you're singing that song and\n我喜欢你唱那首歌时候的样子\nI got a lump in my throat because\n我突然感到哽咽 因为\nYou're gonna sing the words wrong\n你会把同样的歌词再唱错一遍\n——Vancouver Sleep Clinic/ Pop Goes Ambient《Riptide》\n私人约稿禁一切\nuid100010333", "timestamp": "2026-05-20T11:27:56.923000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}, {"emoji": "1nekodrool", "emoji_id": "1206774407562006600", "count": 1}], "attachments": [{"id": "1506619485757374536", "filename": "Image_1779248870575.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 803511, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1506619485262708889/1506619485757374536/Image_1779248870575.png?ex=6a0eec3d&is=6a0d9abd&hm=2a69c7a97aaa5156d58f37b8afac64bf48bfbb680cea77528ba4a3c3a00e112f&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1506619485262708889", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "【戈利亚生贺17h/19:00】Riptide", "forum_channel_id": "1174185304027045969", "thread_tags": ["1441261039227240468"], "is_thread_starter": true}
{"id": "1506598098451824650", "channel_id": "1506598098451824650", "type": 0, "author_id": "1356970554027933877", "author_name": "calmdreab", "author_bot": false, "content": "⚠️戈利亚×凯刻斯CP向⚠️\n我在日落时分遇见你\n晚风变成故事的伏笔\n我想趁着风还没有停\n穿过人潮慢慢靠近你\n——陈抒妮《黄昏等你》\n私人约稿禁一切\nuid100010333", "timestamp": "2026-05-20T10:02:57.910000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}, {"emoji": "1nekodrool", "emoji_id": "1206774407562006600", "count": 1}], "attachments": [{"id": "1506598098841899130", "filename": "Image_1779248246250.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 515498, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1506598098451824650/1506598098841899130/Image_1779248246250.png?ex=6a0ed852&is=6a0d86d2&hm=5c247dfea3e51adb4a7c259c7f6592afc72b809a02fbd9fcc6d9c9bc617e38a3&"}, {"id": "1506598099412455476", "filename": "Image_1779248246912.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 475601, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1506598098451824650/1506598099412455476/Image_1779248246912.png?ex=6a0ed852&is=6a0d86d2&hm=e03dc421589850ab9e7f9d5d3c1eaf878b53a93a50aeae19174be17dc7d55070&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1506598098451824650", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "【戈利亚生贺17h/18:00】黄昏等你", "forum_channel_id": "1174185304027045969", "thread_tags": ["1441261039227240468"], "is_thread_starter": true}
{"id": "1506584513772257401", "channel_id": "1506584513772257401", "type": 0, "author_id": "1356970554027933877", "author_name": "calmdreab", "author_bot": false, "content": "⚠️戈利亚×凯刻斯CP向⚠️\nI don't think I realise\n或许我自己都未曾察觉\nJust how much I miss you sometimes\n对你的思念竟汹涌至此\nWe were young and so in love\n那时我们还年轻 爱得纯真热烈\nWe were just creatures in Heaven\n仿佛抵达云端 宛若天国的造物\n——Glass Animals《Creatures in Heaven》\n私人约稿禁一切\nuid100010333", "timestamp": "2026-05-20T09:08:59.070000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "❤️", "emoji_id": null, "count": 3}, {"emoji": "1nekodrool", "emoji_id": "1206774407562006600", "count": 1}], "attachments": [{"id": "1506584515144056912", "filename": "Image_1779248240609.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 750743, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1506584513772257401/1506584515144056912/Image_1779248240609.png?ex=6a0ecbab&is=6a0d7a2b&hm=1737dac5a807600789be39821874e9bb59283249999f0fc22c1177a778146eb8&"}, {"id": "1506584516192505987", "filename": "Image_1779248241381.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 676951, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1506584513772257401/1506584516192505987/Image_1779248241381.png?ex=6a0ecbab&is=6a0d7a2b&hm=a72529fc8d3ca432c15c064a7c07c8c7ff3183113a3ba672bc46e6baf0d1fe02&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1506584513772257401", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "【戈利亚生贺17h/17:00】Creatures in Heaven", "forum_channel_id": "1174185304027045969", "thread_tags": ["1441261039227240468"], "is_thread_starter": true}
{"id": "1506567183294140466", "channel_id": "1506567183294140466", "type": 0, "author_id": "1356970554027933877", "author_name": "calmdreab", "author_bot": false, "content": "The wine, the beer, the whiskey\n葡萄酒、啤酒、威士忌\nAre the only things that fix me\n是唯一能麻醉我的东西\nI'm not sayin' it's a problem, I can stop it if I wanna\n我不是说这是个问题，如果我想，我可以停下来\nBut the wine, the beer, the whiskey\n但是葡萄酒、啤酒、威士忌\nThey always get me\n他们总是抓住我的心\n——Little Big Town《Wine, Beer, Whiskey》\n画师：章狼大王傅狰\n私人约稿禁一切\nuid100010333", "timestamp": "2026-05-20T08:00:07.162000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 4}, {"emoji": "1nekodrool", "emoji_id": "1206774407562006600", "count": 2}], "attachments": [{"id": "1506567183558246591", "filename": "Image_1779248049727.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 1739543, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1506567183294140466/1506567183558246591/Image_1779248049727.png?ex=6a0f6447&is=6a0e12c7&hm=1f0e7c43332791361341c62c1cf6391137c4907034c27e8f5eedc4346a0490d7&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1506567183294140466", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "【戈利亚生贺17h/16:00】Wine, Beer, Whiskey", "forum_channel_id": "1174185304027045969", "thread_tags": ["1441261039227240468"], "is_thread_starter": true}
